This is a one-page introduction to Emergent Evaluation, also known as Action Evaluation and in the literature Developmental Evaluation.

It is intended for clients exploring this option, while also being useful to students and others learning about evaluation approaches.

This is my best short-format distillation of the literature today on Developmental, and also shows where I am with visual presentation.
